# Cursor/Automation Rules (summary)

- Use AGENTS.md as the single source of truth.
- Do not edit code or run commits without user approval.
- If a change touches >7 files, open a plan under .opencode/commands/.
- Always include provenance lines in commits/PRs.
- For environment access: prefer app-config.ts / lib/env.ts over process.env.

-- Canonicalized from docs/AGENTS-CANONICAL.md on 2026-04-17 as part of unify-agent-docs operation.
